Package: pmed
Title: Accelerate RWD data analysis
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: 
     person("Teague","Tian",email = "nicheerfeng@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3994-1679"))
Description: An R package for building virtual datasets to simulate real world
      medical data in actual production environment, which are mainly used for 
      related research of RWD projects, including accelerating data analysis 
      and providing optimized batch functions.
